body.name: LOVEVOOK Laptop Tote Bag for Women with Insulated Cooler Lunch Compartment, Fits 15.6 Inch Laptop Waterproof Leak-proof Large Capacity Handbag with Purse for Work, Business, Office, Nurse, Purple
features: 【2-in-1 Women's Bag for Lunch bag or Laptop bag】This versatile bag features a unique baffle design to protect food from being crushed by heavy items. When not carrying food, fold down the insulation for extra space in the main pocket, making it perfect for carrying more items.

【Insulated & Leak-proof Cooler Function】The 15.6" laptop lunch tote bag keeps food warm for 5 hours and cold drinks for 10 hours (with ice packs). Its insulated lunch compartment keeps meals fresh and warm, perfect for lunch-bringers.

【Versatility】 This lunch bag offers ample space and compartments. The lower lunch partition measures 14.5"x6"x5.5", easily fitting your daily food and fruit. The upper space can hold your laptop, charger, notebook, and stationery. Tailored specifically for busy professional women, the laptop bag keeps everything organized and easily accessible.

【Matching Wallet Included】Stay organized and stylish with the 8.6"x5.1" wallet, designed for cash, cards, and IDs. It complements the laptop tote bag, providing a coordinated and convenient all-in-one solution.

【MULTIPURPOSE】Add elegance to your work attire with this stylish Quilted women's computer bag. Perfect for more occasions such as college, work, beaches, pinic, camping etc. This cooler lunch bag is a perfect choice for Mother's Day gift, Birthday gift, Valentine's Day gift, Christmas gift etc

2 in 1 Design - How to Use the Baffle This versatile handbag can be effortlessly transformed between a lunch bag and a laptop tote. The unique baffle design in the middle allows you to carry your laptop, power bank, keys, A4 files, water bottles, umbrellas, and other essentials while accommodating your lunch. When you're not using the lunch compartment, simply fold down the flap to create a spacious women's computer tote that's perfect for all your needs.

Fits 15.6 Inch Laptop This bag is designed to securely hold a 15.6-inch laptop, ensuring you can comfortably carry your device for work or leisure. Multi-Pocket Design This bag features numerous pockets for organization, providing ample space for your belongings and easy access to essentials when needed. Sturdy Zippers The bag is equipped with durable zippers that ensure smooth operation and long-lasting performance, keeping your belongings safe and secure. Water-Resistant Made from protective materials, this bag safeguards your belongings from spills or rain, keeping essentials dry and secure.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Stylish and practical!
reviews.reviewText: For a long time, I was looking for a lunchbox that looked like a purse. And I was finding them for sure! But they were all too small, had no pockets or compartments to store anything extra, and overall would’ve been just another bag to have to carry to work. I hate the idea of carrying more than one bag (especially during the winter when you’re also carrying a coat all over the place.)So, there are lunchboxes that look like purses… and then I found this ACTUAL PURSE that HAS A LUNCHBOX COMPARTMENT… but it’s A PURSE! It FITS THINGS! It has POCKETS ON THE INSIDE! And it’s huge! And can carry my laptop! Like what else can I even want from it? This is the ultimate all-in-one purse!I hadn’t noticed from the pictures that it came with a strap for it to be a crossbody too - that was a game changer for me and a nice surprise when I opened the package!The quality seems good, the bag is very stylish, and it has a lot of space whether you’re using the lunchbox compartment or not. It also fits my computer perfectly which I LOVE! So now I’m able to carry all of my food (this tote fits a good amount!), my chargers, my computer, my makeup and more, ALL IN ON BAG!It was very well packaged, and it even came with a storage bag with the brand’s logo so you can store it nicely in the closet and protect it while you’re not using it, just like luxury brands do. Very nice.This is perfect. I absolutely love it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewText: THIS BAG IS FREAKING INCREDIBLE! a lunch box IN your purse? AMAZING! I absolutely LOVE that it has a little shelf you can velcro to the opposite side of the purse inside to keep stuff from sitting directly on top of the lunch box portion. I have a Microsoft pro with an expandable file folder that I can slide into the pocket with tons of space for bigger laptops if needed. ORRR keep stuff separated from the main compartment when im not carrying my laptop. The side pockets are perfect for my Chapstick, gum, pens, etc. And it comes with a very decent sized bag/clutch/whatever the heck you want to call it. I'm a simple small wallet person but always have to have my Chapstick, keys, gum with me. This holds it plenty well with room to spare if I wanted to carry along some makeup too. NOW THIS LUNCH BOX WILL COLLAPSE AND GO OFF TO THE SIDE IF YOU JUST WANT TO USE THE WHOLE PURSE! Did I know that? I don't think so when I ordered but let me tell you.... I WAS SHOOKETH TO MY CORE in the best way! This bag is PERFECT FOR MY NEEDS. WHICH is literally an every day for ALL THE THINGS! work? Yup. Day trip? No problem! Son's all day wrestling tournament? GOT ROOM FOR THAT! we always load up on snacks to take to stay away from concessions. My husband wanted to take his leftover pizza for the tournament today. LADIES AND GENTLEMEN: THAT IS A WHOLE LARGE HANDTOSSED PIZZA IN THERE! To take with. To eat WHENEVER! Along with my pb&j sandwich, baby carrots, 2 small bags of cashews, and FOUR FREAKIMG CUTIES. I could've put more and I almost wanted to but gotta keep my figure so I had to tone down my new purse excitement.THIS IS THEEEEE BAG! You want this. You will be so excited when it gets delivered that you run home on your lunch break just to get it and start using it immediately. You will ALSO walk around your entire place of employment to show it off and make everyone so super jealous that they haven't found this FREAKING GEM first. You'll even make your male boss ooo & aaaah over it just to make sure everyone is well aware that it is a big deal and BRILLIANT to HAVE A LURSE! which is what I called it. Lunch purse.But really, get this. Freaking. Get. This. BEST PURCHASE EVER! I'm officially a ONE BAG FOR ALL THE THINGS wife/mom/everything. Forrrrrget about a bag and a lunch box. WHAT. A. TIME. TO. BE. ALIVE.
